{
  "page": "Warden of the West",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2; text-align:center;\">Warden of the West</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:David_Griffith_Warden_of_the_West.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Warden of the West, by David Griffith © Fantasy Flight Games\"><img alt=\"Warden of the West, by David Griffith © Fantasy Flight Games\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a8/David_Griffith_Warden_of_the_West.png/400px-David_Griffith_Warden_of_the_West.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"268\" srcset=\"/images/a/a8/David_Griffith_Warden_of_the_West.png 1.5x\" /></a><div style=\"font-size: 100%; margin-bottom:10px;\">Warden of the West, by David Griffith © Fantasy Flight Games</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Office</th><td>\nSupreme general in western <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Current Holder</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Daven_Lannister\" title=\"Daven Lannister\">Daven Lannister</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">First Holder</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Loren_I_Lannister\" title=\"Loren I Lannister\">Loren Lannister</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Creator</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Created</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Warden of the West</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Warden\" title=\"Warden\">warden</a> title traditionally held by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a>, the Lords of <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a> and rulers of the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>, on behalf of the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The warden has been responsible for the defense of the western lands of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a> since <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Responsibilities\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Responsibilities</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Known_Wardens_of_the_West\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known Wardens of the West</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Responsibilities\">Responsibilities</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_West&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Responsibilities\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Warden of the West is tasked with defending the western regions of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a> from invaders.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rssm1212.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rssm1212.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Although now part of the realm, men from the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a> historically raided the shores of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sunset_Sea\" title=\"Sunset Sea\">Sunset Sea</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> and some <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> desire a return to the <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Way\" title=\"Old Way\">Old Way</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_West&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Loren_Kneels_HBO.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b0/Loren_Kneels_HBO.png/400px-Loren_Kneels_HBO.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"234\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b0/Loren_Kneels_HBO.png/600px-Loren_Kneels_HBO.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b0/Loren_Kneels_HBO.png/800px-Loren_Kneels_HBO.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Loren_Kneels_HBO.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Loren_I_Lannister\" title=\"Loren I Lannister\">Loren the Last</a> bends the knee to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>, as depicted in <i>Game of Thrones</i>: <i>Histories &amp; Lore</i>.</div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Loren_I_Lannister\" title=\"Loren I Lannister\">Loren I Lannister</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Rock\" title=\"King of the Rock\">King of the Rock</a>, was captured the day after the <a href=\"/index.php/Field_of_Fire\" title=\"Field of Fire\">Field of Fire</a> during <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>. Loren the Last submitted to King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a>, and was named the first Warden of the West.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>, Warden of the West, and Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_North\" title=\"Warden of the North\">Warden of the North</a>, supported King <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a> during <a href=\"/index.php/Greyjoy%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Greyjoy&#39;s Rebellion\">Greyjoy's Rebellion</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_old_way_and_the_new.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_old_way_and_the_new.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_West&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_West&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Aleksander_Karcz_Wardens_of_the_WestIII.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0f/Aleksander_Karcz_Wardens_of_the_WestIII.jpg/400px-Aleksander_Karcz_Wardens_of_the_WestIII.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"165\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0f/Aleksander_Karcz_Wardens_of_the_WestIII.jpg/600px-Aleksander_Karcz_Wardens_of_the_WestIII.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0f/Aleksander_Karcz_Wardens_of_the_WestIII.jpg/800px-Aleksander_Karcz_Wardens_of_the_WestIII.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Aleksander_Karcz_Wardens_of_the_WestIII.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>, Warden of the West, by Aleksander Karcz © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>, Warden of the West and <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, is murdered by his son <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_the_Hand\" title=\"Tower of the Hand\">Tower of the Hand</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos77.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos77.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_West&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Regent\" title=\"Regent\">Queen Regent</a>, wants her uncle, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Kevan_Lannister\" title=\"Kevan Lannister\">Kevan Lannister</a>, to succeed her father as Hand, but Kevan insists he will only do so if he is named regent in her place and she removes herself to <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> Cersei instead names Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harys_Swyft\" title=\"Harys Swyft\">Harys Swyft</a> as Hand, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Damion_Lannister\" title=\"Damion Lannister\">Damion Lannister</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">castellan</a> of the Rock, and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Daven_Lannister\" title=\"Daven Lannister\">Daven Lannister</a> as Warden of the West.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Daven participates in the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Riverrun\" title=\"Siege of Riverrun\">siege of Riverrun</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Wardens_of_the_West\">Known Wardens of the West</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_West&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Wardens of the West\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Loren_Lannister\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Loren Lannister\">Loren Lannister</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/1_AC\" title=\"1 AC\">1&#160;AC</a>-?)</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lyman_Lannister\" title=\"Lyman Lannister\">Lyman Lannister</a> (?&#8211;<a href=\"/index.php/59_AC\" title=\"59 AC\">59&#160;AC</a>)</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tymond_Lannister\" title=\"Tymond Lannister\">Tymond Lannister</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Lannister\" title=\"Jason Lannister\">Jason Lannister</a> (?&#8211;<a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a>)</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Loreon_Lannister_(son_of_Jason)\" title=\"Loreon Lannister (son of Jason)\">Loreon Lannister</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a>-?)</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Lannister_(lord)\" title=\"Damon Lannister (lord)\">Damon Lannister</a> (?&#8211;<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_210_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">210&#160;AC</a>)</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tybolt_Lannister\" title=\"Tybolt Lannister\">Tybolt Lannister</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_210_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">210</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">212&#160;AC</a>)</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Lannister\" title=\"Gerold Lannister\">Gerold Lannister</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_213_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">213</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_244_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">244&#160;AC</a>)</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tytos_Lannister\" title=\"Tytos Lannister\">Tytos Lannister</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_244_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">244</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_267_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">267&#160;AC</a>)</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_267_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">267</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a>)</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Daven_Lannister\" title=\"Daven Lannister\">Daven Lannister</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a>&#8211;)</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_West&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Kingslayer. An able and courageous man, no doubt, but <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">his father</a> is Warden of the West, Robert. In time Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime</a> will succeed to that honor. No one man should hold both <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_East\" title=\"Warden of the East\">East</a> and West.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin</a> the proud and splendid, Warden of the West, <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, oh, what a great man that one is, him and his <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> this and gold that and <a href=\"/index.php/Lion\" title=\"Lion\">lions</a> here and lions there. I'll wager you, he eats too many beans, he breaks wind just like me, but you'll never hear him admit it, oh, no.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Kevan_Lannister\" title=\"Kevan Lannister\">Kevan</a> should be the Warden of the West. Or you. It's not that I'm not grateful for the honor, mind you, but our uncle's twice my age and has more experience of command. I hope he knows I never asked for this.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Daven_Lannister\" title=\"Daven Lannister\">Daven Lannister</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_West&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot12.7